      &lt;p&gt;I was honored to be interviewed by &lt;a href=&#34;https://mobile.twitter.com/thinkingserious&#34;&gt;Elmer Thomas&lt;/a&gt; for SendGrid&amp;rsquo;s very cool &lt;a href=&#34;https://soundcloud.com/somecodingrequired&#34;&gt;Some Coding Required&lt;/a&gt; podcast. We talked about my favorite open source project, how open source has impacted my life, and gave some advice for open source contributors and maintainers.&lt;/p&gt;
